cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper involves the comparison of two popular Big Data engines for processing neuroimaging pipelines, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
